---Spring Update - ChinCapuV1.1---
Spring is here, and so are some exciting new updates in ChinCapu!

New Features:

- Fixed Monsters: The monsters are back and better than ever! Get ready for more thrilling encounters with fully functional enemies.

Spring Cosmetics: Freshen up your look with new seasonal cosmetics, including flower crowns, bunny ears, and colorful accessories to celebrate the season!

- Rig Fixes: We’ve smoothed out the character rigs for better animations and more fluid movement, making your gameplay even more enjoyable.

- Bug Fixes:

Enhanced character control and animation flow for smoother gameplay.

Jump into ChinCapu now and enjoy all the springtime fun! We can’t wait to see you rocking the new cosmetics and tackling the fixed monsters!
